---
title: Herby Stracciatella Farro Bowl with Balsamic Roasted Grapes and Peas
description: The key to a great salad is balance. Our farro bowl uses grapes for sweetness, snap peas for crunch, and a creamy dollop of basil Stracciatella to bring it all together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/herby-stracciatella-farro-bowl-ea72db61.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/herby-stracciatella-farro-bowl-5d7118759ef28c001772fb8b-a6277cf6.pdf
servings: 2
